%description
Implements Bayesian inference for the conditional genetic stock
identification model.  It allows inference of mixed fisheries and also
simulation of mixtures to predict accuracy.  A full description of the
underlying methods is available in a recently published article in the
Canadian Journal of Fisheries and Aquatic Sciences:
<doi.org/10.1139/cjfas-2018-0016>.

